lead_paragraph: Lee Nguyen scored on a penalty kick and assisted on Femi Hollinger-Janzen's go-ahead goal in the New England Revolution's 2-1 victory over the Seattle Sounders on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Nguyen Has Goal and Assist, Revolution Beat Sounders 2-1
